        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "The Zend Loader component will produce a lot of \"file not found\" warnings because it uses  'fopen' to probe the existence of files.\r\n\r\nInstead of using fopen directly, why not use file_exists first to test for the existence and then use 'fopen' to open the files??\r\n\r\nThis should be an easy fix."
        },
